'''Larry Wall''' is the developer of the [[Perl]] programming language, Wall is also known as the original author of the [[rn]] [[Usenet]] software, and the nearly universally used [[patch]].

He is currently employed by O'Reilly & Associates, publisher of popular [[Unix]] reference books.

